          "title": "Saturday",
          "text": "<b><i class='far fa-clock'></i> 09:00 - 18:00 - Guided Tour Daffodil meadow</b> <br> From Casa Petri will go to a magic place from Carpathians mountains - the protected area 'Daffodil Meadow Negrileasa' where will be a celebration to honour the daffodil bloom. The amazing landscape and the daffodil smell will make an unique experience from this trip. There are a couple of ways to get there (according to the group preference and weather): by car (~30min) followed by a 2 hour walk or by bike on the country road (~4h) – if you don't come with your own bike you can rent one from us.",
